content:
Pinghao Wang is currently a second-year postgraduate student in School of Computer Science and Technology, Zhejiang University of Technology, supervised by Xiaolong Zhou. Before that, he reveived a B.Eng degree of Food Quality and Safety in Southwest Minzu University.
Pinghao Wang has wide research interests in Computer Vision and Data Science, with a focus on visual object tracking. He is devoted to optimizing the performance of tracker by using massive data.
